        "new_rules_in_this_unit": [
            "Use two-way prepositions with the accusative case to describe where something is being moved to (Wohin?), and contract an + das → ans, in + das → ins.",
            "Use stellen, legen, hängen, and setzen with accusative two-way prepositions to describe putting objects somewhere: stellen for vertical placement, legen for horizontal, hängen for hanging, setzen for seating.",
            "Convert any infinitive into a neuter noun by capitalizing it: bügeln → das Bügeln."
        ],
